{"tid":1626910,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"和理非全部同我入嚟 唔好睇完片打完飛機就算撚數","createTime":"2019-10-05T13:36:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T19:57:56.000Z","uid":296269,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7eafc26707b017b020e3b1e58067aba6518f1ba8","tid":1626910,"uid":296269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:36:12.000Z","msg":"你出唔到去行唔緊要，至少<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">唔好睇完片屌完就去瞓</span></span></strong>，拿拿聲嚟幫手搵多啲料、幫手分類，畀文宣用又好，畀第時打官司做證據又好。<br />\n<br />\n你睇下中槍男生畀人插贜，就係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">靠多片、睇多幾次LIVE搵到</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">我哋已經搭好咗個網頁<a href=\"https://hkontheroad.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkontheroad.org%2F&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk5q%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=f293bb9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkontheroad.org/</a>，仲有英文版打國際線<a href=\"https://hkontheroad.org/?lang=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkontheroad.org%2F%3Flang%3Den&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk5q%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=a3f892df\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkontheroad.org/?lang=en</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n只係要多啲人<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">睇多幾次10.1, 10.4 嘅 LIVE 片</span></strong></span>，見到任何POPO打傳媒打議員打女仔片，過嚟呢度報料<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">10.1  -  <a href=\"https://hkontheroad.org/date/2019-10-01\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkontheroad.org%2Fdate%2F2019-10-01&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk5q%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=2d90459d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkontheroad.org/date/2019-10-01</a><br />\n10.4 - <a href=\"https://hkontheroad.org/date/2019-10-04\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkontheroad.org%2Fdate%2F2019-10-04&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk5q%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=f23bdc01\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkontheroad.org/date/2019-10-04</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>有個「提供影片資料」制，入去貼條LINK一秒搞掂</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L33FHKn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL33FHKn.png&h=b05d04a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每個事件都係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">愈多片愈好，最好係傳媒live片因為夠清又多啲人會信</span></span>。民間 backup 片都照殺但要已經PO咗上網 （ youtube / facebook etc) 。<span style=\"color: red;\">如果有 timestamp 就一百分</span> （right click -&gt; copy link at current time ) ）<br />\n<br />\n如果有事件未入，可以又或者入個網頁後襟右下角個黃色 + 號。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YHxWf4u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYHxWf4u.png&h=7ea78f6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又或者用住10.4 「__情況」果啲事件(例：<a href=\"https://hkontheroad.org/date/2019-10-04?event=7htNUkZZiJ5gP7UjP3iF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkontheroad.org%2Fdate%2F2019-10-04%3Fevent%3D7htNUkZZiJ5gP7UjP3iF&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk5q%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=17686b16\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkontheroad.org/date/2019-10-04?event=7htNUkZZiJ5gP7UjP3iF</a>)先， admin 小隊會再分類<br />\n<br />\n==============================<br />\n另外如果你可以每周花三至四小時幫手睇片搵片，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>請加入我哋資料小隊</strong></span></span><br />\n去 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/hkotr_submit_data提交事件，在\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fhkotr_submit_data%E6%8F%90%E4%BA%A4%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk5q%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=5833a945\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/hkotr_submit_data提交事件，在</a> TG id 後面加（我想幫手入資料）or （我想幫手翻譯），我哋就會聯絡你，亦完全唔會過問你嘅身份<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就算唔入谷，請大家都繼續推推推推推 <br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>我哋最新加咗每件事有個分享制</strong></span>，將港共政府啲柒事，一件一件咁畀全世界睇！<br />\n<br />\nTG： @hkontheroad<br />\n有咩新消息會響果度公布。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHeung Gong Yan Ga Yau"},{"pid":"d8a7f732b1485bc8ae280e45213b3eb397d8ee7c","tid":1626910,"uid":158973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:37:28.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"444af5312a2bd76b90e2d30da8d9fe227c97e434","tid":1626910,"uid":325081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:48:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb1c61a18e77f970f52a1c32f2029a2a16ace72e","tid":1626910,"uid":259216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:49:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a523c8c8c3a790805938b815a8be6d8480b1a762","tid":1626910,"uid":325081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:55:13.000Z","msg":"個網有啲片係facebook 連結，使唔使backup 定條片先？<br />\n<br />\n我驚佢剷post 無左條link"},{"pid":"f005071febb15d2319c4d7a3b42a77b3656bc653","tid":1626910,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:53:46.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"ac81431ab426163ff643c7c2ab01a11a338b464f","tid":1626910,"uid":296269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a523c8c8c3a790805938b815a8be6d8480b1a762","tid":1626910,"uid":325081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:55:13.000Z","msg":"個網有啲片係facebook 連結，使唔使backup 定條片先？<br />\n<br />\n我驚佢剷post 無左條link"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:57:56.000Z","msg":"Back up Upload 咗上YouTube先？我唔信佢可以剷哂咁多YouTube 片"}]}